<br />

<br />
Came back pulled 2 warriors and in the middle of them the druids sent me a tell asking for help getting their corpses.
<br />
I tried to drag their bodies but got rooted <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-9.gif" border="0" alt="Crying" hspace="2" />. After much trouble got 2 paladins to come help break zone in and get about 5 total corpses.
<br />

<br />
Killed 2 more Amy's on break in but no whip.
<br />

<br />
So it can be done under 63 but i would recommend getting a group or just waiting till a little higher to try it.
