				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Good idea to start North East<a name="43518"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 1 04 7:56 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>This worked for me...
<br />
Zoning in heading North of the flame circle. FM
<br />
Move North East! Corner . not many mobs here no big thing, chant kite stuff down here.  Corner is clear in about 10 mobs. (take down the Eyes first. They dispell. Just chant kite the others without Psalm then to make it faster.
<br />
Now you can head to the flame ring an pick up stuff from south west of it where amys wander. Bring stuff to the now save corner in the North East. Take down the froggies first. They cast the darn fear spell... if you have just Amys dont need mic in resists, just chant it down.
<br />
If the wandere dont drop it, just head into the fire ring from the east. You will get agrgro some Amys soon.
<br />
Repeat and chant kite them down in North East Corner.
<br />

<br />
Good luck. Ought to be easy... it is much more interesting then hoping for that darn Phinny to spawn and rarely drop that darn Bone...  to solo this (and shiver the first time you try .. thinking its a piece of cake later..) is what epics are made for.</span></td>
